**mcp-guide: Project Setup**

Your project preferences are not configured. Guided onboarding takes a few
minutes and covers:

- Language and framework
- Workflow mode
- Methodology preferences (TDD, SOLID, YAGNI, etc.)
- Testing, code quality, and review posture
- Git operations and commit format
- Style and toolchain

To get started, run:

```
{{@}}guide :onboard
```

Or use {{#resource}}_onboard{{/resource}}

To skip and configure manually instead:

```
{{@}}guide :onboard --skip
```

Or use {{#resource}}_onboard?skip{{/resource}}
